==Personal life == From 1921 to his death in 1938, Woolsey was married to Mignonne Park Reed, who lived on to age 94.<ref name=Grave>{{cite web|title=Mignonne R Reed Woolsey (1894-1989) FindAGrave Memorial|url=https://www.findagrave.com/memorial/85552450|publisher=Ancestry.com|accessdate=31 March 2013}}</ref><ref name=IMDb>{{cite web|title=Robert Woolsey-Biography|url=https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0941298/bio|publisher=IMDb.com Inc|accessdate=31 March 2013}}</ref>
==DVD releases == Nine of Wheeler and Woolsey's 21 movies were released in a DVD collection entitled "Wheeler & Woolsey: RKO Comedy Classics Collection" in March 2013 by [[Warner Archive]].<ref name=NYTimes>{{cite news|last=Kehr|first=Dave|title=DVD Ribaldry Before the Code|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/03/24/movies/homevideo/new-dvds-wheeler-and-woolseys-rko-comedy-classics.html?pagewanted=all|accessdate=30 March 2013|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2 March 2013}}</ref>
{U.S. Census Records indicate he was born in Carbondale, Jackson Co, IL}
